definitions.definition: ( fandom slang ) A person who is a stan ( “ obsessive fan ” ) of multiple people or things , especially K-pop performers .

main_definition: ( fandom slang ) A person who is a stan ( “ obsessive fan ” ) of multiple people or things , especially K-pop performers .

definitions.definition: A proposed special territory in apartheid -era South Africa in which racial laws are repealed and the authority of the central government is reduced , advocated as a policy by Paul N. Malherbe.

main_definition: ( South Africa , historical ) A proposed special territory in apartheid -era South Africa in which racial laws are repealed and the authority of the central government is reduced , advocated as a policy by Paul N. Malherbe.
